    What is the cost of old age home in Pune?
    The cost of living at this old age home in Pune depends upon the type of accommodation. The price of a single room starts at INR 7,000 whereas the price of a double room starts at INR 10,000 per month.

    What do you mean by old age home?
    An old age home, also called a retirement home, is a residential facility with nursing and assisted living facilities designed for older adults. They receive the necessary assistance and care, from meals, housekeeping, medical care, and recreational activities to maintain their quality of life.19 Apr 2023
